# PathcraftAI Auto Patch Monitor - Crontab Configuration
# Add this to your crontab with: crontab patch_monitor.crontab
#
# GGG Patch Schedule (NZ timezone):
# - Major patches: Wed/Thu morning (9 AM NZ = 5 AM Korea = 4 PM UTC-1day)
# - Hotfixes: Any time (usually within 24h of major patch)
#
# Strategy: Check every 6 hours to catch patches ASAP
# Cost: ~$0.04/day (4 checks * $0.01 GPT-4 analysis)

# Environment variables (set these in your shell profile or here)
# DISCORD_WEBHOOK_PATCHES=your_webhook_url
# YOUTUBE_API_KEY=your_youtube_key
# PATHCRAFT_OPENAI_KEY=your_openai_key
# TWITTER_BEARER_TOKEN=your_twitter_token (optional)
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_reddit_id (optional)
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_reddit_secret (optional)

# Check every 6 hours (4 times per day)
0 */6 * * * cd /path/to/Pathcraft-AI/src/PathcraftAI.Parser && /usr/bin/python3 patch_monitor_cron.py >> patch_monitor_cron.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Check only during GGG patch windows (more cost-effective)
# NZ Morning (9 AM NZ = 5 AM Korea)
# 0 5 * * 3,4 cd /path/to/Pathcraft-AI/src/PathcraftAI.Parser && /usr/bin/python3 patch_monitor_cron.py >> patch_monitor_cron.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Check every 12 hours (2 times per day, cheaper)
# 0 0,12 * * * cd /path/to/Pathcraft-AI/src/PathcraftAI.Parser && /usr/bin/python3 patch_monitor_cron.py >> patch_monitor_cron.log 2>&1
